From: Thomas Gleixner <tglx@linutronix.de>
Date: Sat, 25 Feb 2017 10:27:37 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] mac80211_hwsim: Replace bogus hrtimer clockid
Git-commit: 8fbcfeb8a9cc803464d6c166e7991913711c612c
Patch-mainline: 4.11-rc1
References: bsc#1047651

mac80211_hwsim initializes a hrtimer with clockid
CLOCK_MONOTONIC_RAW. That's not supported.

Use CLOCK_MONOTONIC instead.

Signed-off-by: Thomas Gleixner <tglx@linutronix.de>
Signed-off-by: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

